author: psiwebtn
title: On This Date
text:
On This Date Friday, October 9, 2015 
October 9, 2009 - Casey Lawrence throws for two touchdowns and runs for two others to help Panther Valley roll past Marian, 47-14, in an Anthracite Football League contest. Lawrence completes 8-of-15 passes for 148 yards. He tosses a 30-yard TD strike to Jeff Corby and a 27-yard scoring pass to Ryan Poeldnurk. Lawrence also collects 141 yards on the ground. Kyle McAvoy adds 72 yards rushing, including scoring runs of 11 and four yards. The winners, coached by Frank Damian, also receive a 64-yard TD run from Joe Revell.
